Firefox 2.0.0.19 Portable by ManjaroLover153

This project repackages Mozilla Firefox 2.0.0.19 into a portable, installer-free format for archival, educational, and legacy compatibility purposes.

All original Firefox binaries and assets remain copyright © Mozilla Foundation and are licensed under the Mozilla Public License Version 1.1.

This repackaging is provided "as-is", without any warranty. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by Mozilla.

⚠ WARNING: Firefox 2.0.0.19 is outdated and contains multiple unpatched vulnerabilities. Do not use it for modern web browsing.

